data.eml:eml: Stenocyphon neozealandicus, a new species from New Zealand of a previously monotypic subfamily from Chile (Coleoptera: Scirtidae: Stenocyphoninae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Ruta, Rafał, Thorpe, Stephen, Yoshitomi, Hiroyuki (2011): Stenocyphon neozealandicus, a new species from New Zealand of a previously monotypic subfamily from Chile (Coleoptera: Scirtidae: Stenocyphoninae). Zootaxa 3113: 65-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.205536
